txt.en: You have defeated the Uruk-hai raiding party, and protected the Beacon Hills and the Rohirrim from their blades and arrows.

An elite raiding party of Uruk-hai can be found in the eastern edge of the Beacon Hills.\n\nYou should defeat the Uruk-hai raiding party.
